high_descs: Go left and walk to the stove, turn toward the cabinet on your left.

Open the microwave and put the knife inside.
Turn right and walk toward the door, then turn right and walk to the white table.
Pick up a slice of bread.

Put the knife inside the microwave.
Head right and go back to the table with the bread on it.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Go right and head back to the microwave.
Put the bread in the microwave with the knife and turn it on.
Take the bread out of the microwave and go to the black cabinet to the right of the microwave.
Open the bottom cabinet and put the bread inside, then close the cabinet.

Put the knife in the microwave
